Released MOBs are on hostile or neutral flagged to you and all others. they then immediately seek their spawn area. if they are IN their spawn area, sometimes they stay neutral for a set amount of time. Some however immediately go back to aggro after reaching their spawn area. not sure if this is a bug or not. It is completely different with each MOB and depend on location (ie, how close to their spawn you release them).<P>Post any detailed info anyone has on this and i will see if soemone can track down any trends for us.<P>--------------------<P>i3ullseye<BR>"You're good, but me? I'm Magic!"<P>Rictus -Sorceror(DAOC)/Rictus(EQ)<BR>DAOC Sorceror team lead...<P>Please visit our <A HREF="http://www.yesterdayland.com/popopedia/shows/toys/ty1050.php" TARGET=_blank>Sponsors!</A>  <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0">
