Did lots of experimenting with all kinds of pets a while back.<P>Buff casting pets will attack you IF you release them when there in the middle of casting a buff on you. So if you have your own AF buff and iso clerics keeps trying to cast his AF buff on you and you release him he will attack you.<P>If your pet seems to be in combat mode all the time and dosent get the run speed just put him in passive for about 20 secs and hell go back to normal.<P>--------------------<P>Melaron<BR>50 Sorcerer, Gawaine
